{"tid":95110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同ex出完去 感覺唔知點咁","createTime":"2017-01-25T18:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T02:41:44.000Z","uid":6371,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71b221f4c44158f76503f5388cb663f3dc4584c0","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"我同個ex係幾年前散左之後都無咩點搵大家 呢排傾番下之後大家話約出黎聚下<br />\n前幾日就同ex兩個人出左去食下野 之後周圍行左陣<br />\n都幾開心 好似以前拍拖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過就完全無拖手果d<br />\n<br />\n去完之後開始掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但我完全唔知佢點諗 又唔知佢宜家有無仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同佢message佢又有少少cool咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有無巴打有類似經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪應該試下再約佢 睇下佢出唔出？"},{"pid":"ea5a37ec748520d01fee5935d96b3a2447bb4697","tid":95110,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T18:47:22.000Z","msg":"你都有答案啦<br />\n係對人有feel既去馬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b6a63ba5744afef49b3241bce446c247cf66a1","tid":95110,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T18:53:54.000Z","msg":"打返場友誼波"},{"pid":"3de0edc53b4f82588661f11f34ccc8f70abd909d","tid":95110,"uid":70415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T18:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打返場友誼波</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />舊車放耐左一定要試試副偈先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1815e866d306ad3dc325e61a94a38ee506648925","tid":95110,"uid":27830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:00:58.000Z","msg":"再約囉"},{"pid":"1d27190fa297cd8948ac071b13271f13b8ba53b0","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:05:23.000Z","msg":"其實好想知佢宜家有無仔 唔知點開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n約出黎先問 定係問左先好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5c5c6bee83fe770e3e13a21abfa5589fc9660e","tid":95110,"uid":27830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T19:14:09.000Z","msg":"認真唔好急慢慢嚟"},{"pid":"79028da683627f51d253b37a703032f092cc1727","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T00:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真唔好急慢慢嚟</blockquote><br />\n姐係唔好問住 再約左出黎先睇下點？"},{"pid":"9c020b598427603b7b498a78c4593d5b6ccc6ecf","tid":95110,"uid":27830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T00:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真唔好急慢慢嚟</blockquote><br />\n姐係唔好問住 再約左出黎先睇下點？</blockquote><br />\n約多幾次先或者你問得好啲<br />\n反正唔好比佢覺得你得佢一個"},{"pid":"d0220d072127ba46c77aada50f0b019cf7d47f29","tid":95110,"uid":36867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T00:37:21.000Z","msg":"點解之前要散"},{"pid":"5016b997618d1c6b922d140c67384fb613f3de6e","tid":95110,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T19:43:42.000Z","msg":"求勵志故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣係佢話散？<br />\n一齊幾耐分左幾耐？<br />\n你地宜家幾多歲？<br />\n散左呢幾年你地有無拍拖？"},{"pid":"9430ca85dc6416d173e3fb069f10814f9fabc557","tid":95110,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T19:46:58.000Z","msg":"比啲時間啦<br />\n友誼波唔係一日練成"},{"pid":"f5aa2a3025d5edb9d9d41c6fa7ae952a9721f5c9","tid":95110,"uid":58002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:39:58.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4173c46196c8b60d7bd01d0266c1e494ddec2e","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T01:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求勵志故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣係佢話散？<br />\n一齊幾耐分左幾耐？<br />\n你地宜家幾多歲？<br />\n散左呢幾年你地有無拍拖？</blockquote><br />\n果陣仲讀緊書 係我話散 我都唔係好記得點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一齊左一年左右<br />\n宜家我同佢都22歲 散左之後大家都有拍過拖"},{"pid":"2eade9f8df7c0ee2da31d98695ed9993614a6cd6","tid":95110,"uid":42728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解之前要散</blockquote><br />\n我都想問<br />\n之前既問題係唔會因為時間耐左而自動修正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586c273d037ada4aa506429a91a640dd75b0a1c0","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T01:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比啲時間啦<br />\n友誼波唔係一日練成</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係未試過打友誼波"},{"pid":"1f6518fa02c678e2d45b57209ee1c3a6c259f513","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解之前要散</blockquote><br />\n我都想問<br />\n之前既問題係唔會因為時間耐左而自動修正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果陣我話散 <br />\n應該係嘈過下 之後就過多排散左 確實原因唔係好記得 果陣好忙 之後大家都無搵番大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299dcd30a755a016eaa5d47d33f6c215263d9bc8","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T01:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afb7a627ea7436f5bb5c6b0db0df3c26ce19cae","tid":95110,"uid":33737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"巴打同你差唔多一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3143493e5318f03c62f914b696669f4d6a6d087","tid":95110,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:22:50.000Z","msg":"去馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連咩事分手都唔記得姐係唔係重要事啦<br />\n但你要諗下係純粹寂寞想有人陪 定真係鍾意"},{"pid":"bac55ef2b525dcb3a24eab395ea7a3ae9734d262","tid":95110,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:23:55.000Z","msg":"咁咪做返朋友順手打下友誼波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3b0a3bffd6e1e65586cc65a7be4f938af8973b","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連咩事分手都唔記得姐係唔係重要事啦<br />\n但你要諗下係純粹寂寞想有人陪 定真係鍾意</blockquote><br />\n你咁講 其實我都唔係好肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2dbef4086c93f806369b01fd9e1ad1f44e44e55","tid":95110,"uid":52026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"係咪真係想追自己feel到啦<br />\n不過你形容得好普通<br />\n同邊條女兩個行街都開心架啦....如果條女ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808f8f035ac686ad33298be929955bfd005560a0","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁咪做返朋友順手打下友誼波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543b9d3a52e0110017f1781dc7eff2b535d333b2","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"宜家想再約但唔知點講好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前真係好少搵大家 上次出完咁快又叫佢出去 唔知點問好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4287226abb91e3d679b06bceff37e191eb2dd1b6","tid":95110,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真<br />\n唔知幾多手"},{"pid":"aa1808b25daa3f11ac432244098df245db634d03","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪真係想追自己feel到啦<br />\n不過你形容得好普通<br />\n同邊條女兩個行街都開心架啦....如果條女ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有傾有講幾開心 都算多野傾 又周圍行左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過其實你都岩 換轉係第2個靚女 可能我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ab523c35c709cce90f3015bd32f47968164440","tid":95110,"uid":42728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去馬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連咩事分手都唔記得姐係唔係重要事啦<br />\n但你要諗下係純粹寂寞想有人陪 定真係鍾意</blockquote><br />\n你咁講 其實我都唔係好肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因咩事分手唔記得就去馬啦<br />\n因為寂寞又好 因為鐘意都好<br />\n雙方都無另一半咪拍下先<br />\n後生係咁，唔洗咁介意<br />\n試下試下先知自己想要咩"},{"pid":"9bbe4ca52764f56e42a97c18baa7a8e679d99efd","tid":95110,"uid":6371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm